<h1>FIFA WORLD RANKING SYSTEM DOCUMENTARY</h1>
<div class="col-lg-6">
<h2 class="h1 text-success">INTRODUCTION</h2>
<p>The FIFA world Ranking system an R developed system,mainly used to visualize the worlds best performing countries.<br>
This system can also be used to predict the country's rank according the matches played and their weights as will be explained 
</p>
</div>
