<div class="col-lg-12"><div class="row"><h4 class="text-success">OPPONENT STRENGTH</h4></div>
<div class="row ">
<p class=" p text-left">A win against a very highly ranked opponent is a considerably greater achievement than a win against a low rated opponent ,thus the strength of<br>the oppossing team is an important factor<br />
The formula used is:<br />
Opposition strength multiplier=(200-ranking position)/100</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-lg-12"><div class="row"><h4 class="text-success">REGIONAL STRENGTH</h4></div>
<div class="row">
<table class="table table-dark table-striped">
<tr style="background-color:green; color:white;"><th>Confederation</th><th>After 2014 world cup</th><th>After 2010 world cup</th><th>After 2006 world cup</th><th>Up to and including  2006 world cup</th></tr>
<tr>
